    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you are already using Apache Commons Lang, the  <a href=\"http://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/javadocs/api-release/org/apache/commons/lang3/RandomUtils.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>RandomUtils</code></a>  makes this a one-liner:</p>\n<pre><code>byte[] randomBytes = RandomUtils.nextBytes(20);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Note: this does not produce cryptographically-secure bytes.</p>\n"
  }, {
